_nativeKeysIn.js

This function is like Object.keys except that it includes inherited enumerable properties.

Params
object Object The object to query. 
function nativeKeysIn(object) {
  var result = [];
  if (object != null) {
    for (var key in Object(object)) {
      result.push(key);
    }
  }
  return result;
}

module.exports = nativeKeysIn;
